Crowded beach



For the first time that we can remember, the parking lots were completely full, and the beach was very crowded. It was a beautiful beach day.
Taken Sunday, June 17, 2001, 03:23:18pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 945kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/800s @ F5.6, ISO 100, 377mm
PS6 Curves 45:0 - 80:80 - 200:255, Unsharp Mask 2.0 70%, debloom seagull
